div.span:
After I hung up the phone on you, I listened a little longer
as that thing moved around the lobby. I heard it panting.
And I could hear some kind of clatter on the marble floor.

rect.style: fill: rgb(13, 0, 50); font-family: 'trebuchet ms', verdana, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; line-height: 25.6px; padding-block: 5px; padding: 5px; padding-inline: 5px; stroke: rgb(42, 0, 168); stroke-width: 5px;

g.style: border-block-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); border-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); border-inline-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); caret-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); color: rgb(204, 204, 204); column-rule-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); fill: rgb(13, 0, 50); font-family: 'trebuchet ms', verdana, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; line-height: 25.6px; outline-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); padding-block: 5px; padding: 5px; padding-inline: 5px; stroke: rgb(42, 0, 168); stroke-width: 5px; text-align: center; text-decoration: none solid rgb(204, 204, 204); text-emphasis-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); -webkit-text-fill-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(204, 204, 204);

div.span:
And I realized something else: what kind of hotel manager
hides from a potential guest? You can't spell business
without bravery! Or, eh, something like that.

rect.style: fill: rgb(13, 0, 50); font-family: 'trebuchet ms', verdana, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; line-height: 25.6px; padding-block: 5px; padding: 5px; padding-inline: 5px; stroke: rgb(42, 0, 168); stroke-width: 5px;

g.style: border-block-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); border-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); border-inline-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); caret-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); color: rgb(204, 204, 204); column-rule-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); fill: rgb(13, 0, 50); font-family: 'trebuchet ms', verdana, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; line-height: 25.6px; outline-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); padding-block: 5px; padding: 5px; padding-inline: 5px; stroke: rgb(42, 0, 168); stroke-width: 5px; text-align: center; text-decoration: none solid rgb(204, 204, 204); text-emphasis-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); -webkit-text-fill-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(204, 204, 204);

div.span: I ordered gloves! They should be arriving... shortly.

rect.style: fill: rgb(13, 0, 50); font-family: 'trebuchet ms', verdana, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; line-height: 25.6px; padding-block: 5px; padding: 5px; padding-inline: 5px; stroke: rgb(42, 0, 168); stroke-width: 5px;

g.style: border-block-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); border-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); border-inline-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); caret-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); color: rgb(204, 204, 204); column-rule-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); fill: rgb(13, 0, 50); font-family: 'trebuchet ms', verdana, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; line-height: 25.6px; outline-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); padding-block: 5px; padding: 5px; padding-inline: 5px; stroke: rgb(42, 0, 168); stroke-width: 5px; text-align: center; text-decoration: none solid rgb(204, 204, 204); text-emphasis-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); -webkit-text-fill-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(204, 204, 204);

div.span:
Ah, I haven't opened it yet. But sir, maybe you're an expert
with mysterious boxes, and you know what to expect?

div.span: Opening the doors!

div.span:
I thought I was dying. But then I remembered, I'm already
dead. And the images weren't like memories, but maybe like
some kind of incredibly fast teaser trailer for a movie I'll
never see.

rect.style: fill: rgb(13, 0, 50); font-family: 'trebuchet ms', verdana, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; line-height: 25.6px; padding-block: 5px; padding: 5px; padding-inline: 5px; stroke: rgb(42, 0, 168); stroke-width: 5px;

g.style: border-block-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); border-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); border-inline-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); caret-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); color: rgb(204, 204, 204); column-rule-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); fill: rgb(13, 0, 50); font-family: 'trebuchet ms', verdana, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; line-height: 25.6px; outline-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); padding-block: 5px; padding: 5px; padding-inline: 5px; stroke: rgb(42, 0, 168); stroke-width: 5px; text-align: center; text-decoration: none solid rgb(204, 204, 204); text-emphasis-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); -webkit-text-fill-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(204, 204, 204);

div.span:
Ah. I almost forgot to mention! There's a big, fat box on my
desk. I can only assume it was left here for me by the bird-
dog thing. So maybe it was like a giant carrier pigeon from
Hell.

rect.style: fill: rgb(13, 0, 50); font-family: 'trebuchet ms', verdana, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; line-height: 25.6px; padding-block: 5px; padding: 5px; padding-inline: 5px; stroke: rgb(42, 0, 168); stroke-width: 5px;

g.style: border-block-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); border-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); border-inline-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); caret-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); color: rgb(204, 204, 204); column-rule-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); fill: rgb(13, 0, 50); font-family: 'trebuchet ms', verdana, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; line-height: 25.6px; outline-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); padding-block: 5px; padding: 5px; padding-inline: 5px; stroke: rgb(42, 0, 168); stroke-width: 5px; text-align: center; text-decoration: none solid rgb(204, 204, 204); text-emphasis-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); -webkit-text-fill-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(204, 204, 204);

div.span:
Well it smashed through the other window of the lobby on its
way out, so now I have TWO windows to replace.

rect.style: fill: rgb(13, 0, 50); font-family: 'trebuchet ms', verdana, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; line-height: 25.6px; padding-block: 5px; padding: 5px; padding-inline: 5px; stroke: rgb(42, 0, 168); stroke-width: 5px;

g.style: border-block-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); border-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); border-inline-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); caret-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); color: rgb(204, 204, 204); column-rule-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); fill: rgb(13, 0, 50); font-family: 'trebuchet ms', verdana, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; line-height: 25.6px; outline-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); padding-block: 5px; padding: 5px; padding-inline: 5px; stroke: rgb(42, 0, 168); stroke-width: 5px; text-align: center; text-decoration: none solid rgb(204, 204, 204); text-emphasis-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); -webkit-text-fill-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(204, 204, 204);

div.span:
Ah, just as I expected! But trust me, sir, your luxury suite
on floor 1434 will be the best part.

rect.style: fill: rgb(13, 0, 50); font-family: 'trebuchet ms', verdana, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; line-height: 25.6px; padding-block: 5px; padding: 5px; padding-inline: 5px; stroke: rgb(42, 0, 168); stroke-width: 5px;

g.style: border-block-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); border-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); border-inline-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); caret-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); color: rgb(204, 204, 204); column-rule-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); fill: rgb(13, 0, 50); font-family: 'trebuchet ms', verdana, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; line-height: 25.6px; outline-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); padding-block: 5px; padding: 5px; padding-inline: 5px; stroke: rgb(42, 0, 168); stroke-width: 5px; text-align: center; text-decoration: none solid rgb(204, 204, 204); text-emphasis-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); -webkit-text-fill-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(204, 204, 204);

div.span:
There there, Mr. [playerLastName]. I also want to know how
you died, and this box of classified documents surely hides
the answer. But we can't be too hasty! I'll update you when
I can open it safely.

rect.style: fill: rgb(13, 0, 50); font-family: 'trebuchet ms', verdana, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; line-height: 25.6px; padding-block: 5px; padding: 5px; padding-inline: 5px; stroke: rgb(42, 0, 168); stroke-width: 5px;

g.style: border-block-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); border-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); border-inline-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); caret-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); color: rgb(204, 204, 204); column-rule-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); fill: rgb(13, 0, 50); font-family: 'trebuchet ms', verdana, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; line-height: 25.6px; outline-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); padding-block: 5px; padding: 5px; padding-inline: 5px; stroke: rgb(42, 0, 168); stroke-width: 5px; text-align: center; text-decoration: none solid rgb(204, 204, 204); text-emphasis-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); -webkit-text-fill-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(204, 204, 204);

div.span:
What, you think there's a bomb in it? I appreciate your
concern, sir, but who would want to do that to me? And if it
was a trap, they'd make it pretty--and easy to open.

rect.style: fill: rgb(13, 0, 50); font-family: 'trebuchet ms', verdana, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; line-height: 25.6px; padding-block: 5px; padding: 5px; padding-inline: 5px; stroke: rgb(42, 0, 168); stroke-width: 5px;

g.style: border-block-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); border-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); border-inline-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); caret-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); color: rgb(204, 204, 204); column-rule-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); fill: rgb(13, 0, 50); font-family: 'trebuchet ms', verdana, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; line-height: 25.6px; outline-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); padding-block: 5px; padding: 5px; padding-inline: 5px; stroke: rgb(42, 0, 168); stroke-width: 5px; text-align: center; text-decoration: none solid rgb(204, 204, 204); text-emphasis-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); -webkit-text-fill-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(204, 204, 204);

div.span: Never better, Mr. [playerLastName].

rect.style: fill: rgb(13, 0, 50); font-family: 'trebuchet ms', verdana, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; line-height: 25.6px; padding-block: 5px; padding: 5px; padding-inline: 5px; stroke: rgb(42, 0, 168); stroke-width: 5px;

g.style: border-block-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); border-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); border-inline-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); caret-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); color: rgb(204, 204, 204); column-rule-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); fill: rgb(13, 0, 50); font-family: 'trebuchet ms', verdana, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; line-height: 25.6px; outline-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); padding-block: 5px; padding: 5px; padding-inline: 5px; stroke: rgb(42, 0, 168); stroke-width: 5px; text-align: center; text-decoration: none solid rgb(204, 204, 204); text-emphasis-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); -webkit-text-fill-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(204, 204, 204);

div.span:
That's what I was thinking. If we're right, this box should
contain a complete account of all history that has ever
unfolded, up to the present time. And we should be able to
find out what killed you!

rect.style: fill: rgb(13, 0, 50); font-family: 'trebuchet ms', verdana, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; line-height: 25.6px; padding-block: 5px; padding: 5px; padding-inline: 5px; stroke: rgb(42, 0, 168); stroke-width: 5px;

g.style: border-block-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); border-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); border-inline-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); caret-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); color: rgb(204, 204, 204); column-rule-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); fill: rgb(13, 0, 50); font-family: 'trebuchet ms', verdana, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; line-height: 25.6px; outline-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); padding-block: 5px; padding: 5px; padding-inline: 5px; stroke: rgb(42, 0, 168); stroke-width: 5px; text-align: center; text-decoration: none solid rgb(204, 204, 204); text-emphasis-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); -webkit-text-fill-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(204, 204, 204);

div.span: Sir, if you do the numbers that's 500 images a second.

rect.style: fill: rgb(13, 0, 50); font-family: 'trebuchet ms', verdana, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; line-height: 25.6px; padding-block: 5px; padding: 5px; padding-inline: 5px; stroke: rgb(42, 0, 168); stroke-width: 5px;

g.style: border-block-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); border-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); border-inline-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); caret-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); color: rgb(204, 204, 204); column-rule-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); fill: rgb(13, 0, 50); font-family: 'trebuchet ms', verdana, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; line-height: 25.6px; outline-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); padding-block: 5px; padding: 5px; padding-inline: 5px; stroke: rgb(42, 0, 168); stroke-width: 5px; text-align: center; text-decoration: none solid rgb(204, 204, 204); text-emphasis-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); -webkit-text-fill-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(204, 204, 204);

div.span: I'm sure you had a good time, meantime?

rect.style: fill: rgb(13, 0, 50); font-family: 'trebuchet ms', verdana, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; line-height: 25.6px; padding-block: 5px; padding: 5px; padding-inline: 5px; stroke: rgb(42, 0, 168); stroke-width: 5px;

g.style: border-block-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); border-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); border-inline-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); caret-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); color: rgb(204, 204, 204); column-rule-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); fill: rgb(13, 0, 50); font-family: 'trebuchet ms', verdana, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; line-height: 25.6px; outline-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); padding-block: 5px; padding: 5px; padding-inline: 5px; stroke: rgb(42, 0, 168); stroke-width: 5px; text-align: center; text-decoration: none solid rgb(204, 204, 204); text-emphasis-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); -webkit-text-fill-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(204, 204, 204);

div.span: I'm BACK!

rect.style: fill: rgb(13, 0, 50); font-family: 'trebuchet ms', verdana, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; line-height: 25.6px; padding-block: 5px; padding: 5px; padding-inline: 5px; stroke: rgb(42, 0, 168); stroke-width: 5px;

g.style: border-block-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); border-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); border-inline-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); caret-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); color: rgb(204, 204, 204); column-rule-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); fill: rgb(13, 0, 50); font-family: 'trebuchet ms', verdana, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; line-height: 25.6px; outline-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); padding-block: 5px; padding: 5px; padding-inline: 5px; stroke: rgb(42, 0, 168); stroke-width: 5px; text-align: center; text-decoration: none solid rgb(204, 204, 204); text-emphasis-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); -webkit-text-fill-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(204, 204, 204);

div.span:
Yes, that's what I was thinking! If we're right, this box
should contain a complete account of all history that has
ever unfolded, up to the present time. And we should be able
to find out what killed you!

g.style: border-block-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); border-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); border-inline-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); caret-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); color: rgb(204, 204, 204); column-rule-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); fill: rgb(13, 0, 50); font-family: 'trebuchet ms', verdana, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; line-height: 25.6px; outline-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); padding-block: 5px; padding: 5px; padding-inline: 5px; stroke: rgb(42, 0, 168); stroke-width: 5px; text-align: center; text-decoration: none solid rgb(204, 204, 204); text-emphasis-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); -webkit-text-fill-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(204, 204, 204);

div.span:
Then I decided the best course of action was to curl up in
the fetal position for fifteen minutes, which I promptly did
so.

rect.style: fill: rgb(13, 0, 50); font-family: 'trebuchet ms', verdana, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; line-height: 25.6px; padding-block: 5px; padding: 5px; padding-inline: 5px; stroke: rgb(42, 0, 168); stroke-width: 5px;

g.style: border-block-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); border-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); border-inline-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); caret-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); color: rgb(204, 204, 204); column-rule-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); fill: rgb(13, 0, 50); font-family: 'trebuchet ms', verdana, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; line-height: 25.6px; outline-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); padding-block: 5px; padding: 5px; padding-inline: 5px; stroke: rgb(42, 0, 168); stroke-width: 5px; text-align: center; text-decoration: none solid rgb(204, 204, 204); text-emphasis-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); -webkit-text-fill-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(204, 204, 204);

div.span:
So, I shielded my eyes and stood up with the treat. And I
said, "Here, you want a snack?"

div.span:
What, you think there's a bomb in it? I appreciate your
concern, sir, but who would want to do that to me? And if it
was a trap, they'd make it pretty--and easy to open.

rect.style: fill: rgb(13, 0, 50); font-family: 'trebuchet ms', verdana, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; line-height: 25.6px; padding-block: 5px; padding: 5px; padding-inline: 5px; stroke: rgb(42, 0, 168); stroke-width: 5px;

g.style: border-block-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); border-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); border-inline-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); caret-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); color: rgb(204, 204, 204); column-rule-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); fill: rgb(13, 0, 50); font-family: 'trebuchet ms', verdana, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; line-height: 25.6px; outline-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); padding-block: 5px; padding: 5px; padding-inline: 5px; stroke: rgb(42, 0, 168); stroke-width: 5px; text-align: center; text-decoration: none solid rgb(204, 204, 204); text-emphasis-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); -webkit-text-fill-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(204, 204, 204);

div.span:
No, of course you are. Aha, sir, you almost had me with that
deadpan humor! My hotel is really more of a luxury resort,
and perfectly safe--far better than anything out there.

g.style: border-block-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); border-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); border-inline-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); caret-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); color: rgb(204, 204, 204); column-rule-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); fill: rgb(13, 0, 50); font-family: 'trebuchet ms', verdana, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; line-height: 25.6px; outline-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); padding-block: 5px; padding: 5px; padding-inline: 5px; stroke: rgb(42, 0, 168); stroke-width: 5px; text-align: center; text-decoration: none solid rgb(204, 204, 204); text-emphasis-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); -webkit-text-fill-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(204, 204, 204);

div.span:
No, the dog treats are--I just like the taste, okay? But I
figured I could give one up if it meant befriending this
large, terrifying creature.

g.style: border-block-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); border-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); border-inline-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); caret-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); color: rgb(204, 204, 204); column-rule-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); fill: rgb(13, 0, 50); font-family: 'trebuchet ms', verdana, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; line-height: 25.6px; outline-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); padding-block: 5px; padding: 5px; padding-inline: 5px; stroke: rgb(42, 0, 168); stroke-width: 5px; text-align: center; text-decoration: none solid rgb(204, 204, 204); text-emphasis-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); -webkit-text-fill-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(204, 204, 204);

div.span:
So I stood up and looked over the desk at the strange
creature. That's when a thousand images flashed through my
eyes, all in two seconds.

div.span: Oh, you're not joking, are you? You don't like it here?

div.span:
But this box is covered in slime. I think it's the slobber
of the bird-dog thing. And I'm not touching that.

div.span:
Anyway, it seemed like this strange being might never leave
the lobby. Then I got an idea. I reached for the drawer in
my desk where I keep the dog treats.

div.span: So I thought, "Of course, it must only be a very unusual breed of dog!"

It looks like any other old box. But this one has a special
label. It says, "CLASSIFIED. FROM THE KING'S AIDES, TO THE
TWO CHILDREN IN A TRENCH COAT".

div.span: What do you think that means?

And the treat was torn out of my hand before I knew it!
Then, there was a loud swoop and shattering. I opened my
eyes, and the thing was gone. I think it might have been
more like a bird than a dog. But I think it was both.
